Package ISP.classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimationPanel
    This Panel displays the flash intro to the grame.
    DataBase
    This class stores all the French words and HighScores this game will use.
    Dialogs
    This class is responsible for creating the dialogs.
    FioraGame
    This class is responsible for creating the main menu, drop down menu, and listeners.
    Game
    This class is responsible for the levels and cutscenes.
    GameGraphics
    This class is used to get pictures (Most features were removed).
    MainMenuOptions
    This class is responsible for the main menu options besides New Game.
    MouseTrack
    This class is used to time how long it takes the user to beat the game.
    Sounds
    This class is responsible for playing sounds when the user gets something right or wrong.
    SplashWindow1
    This class displays the splashscreen at the beginning of the program.
    Timer1
    This class is used to time how long it takes the user to beat the game.
